OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782776882
OL,3,CShop price inflation remains unchanged
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of Middle East knock-
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"In clothing and general merchandise,
OL,8,Fretailers responded to the hot weather
OL,9,Fwith promotions across summer
OL,10,Fessentials in clothing, footwear and
OL,11,Flighter household textiles, despite
OL,12,Foverall non-food inflation rising."
OL,14,FMike Watkins, head of retailer and
OL,15,Fbusiness insight at NIQ, said: "Food
OL,16,Finflation remains lower than a year
OL,17,Fago helped by price reductions and
OL,18,Fhigher levels of promotion.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@cO]wD@`OU
