OL,3,CShop price inflation remains unchanged
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of Middle East knock-
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"There was also some downward pressure
OL,8,Fon prices in non food seasonal
OL,9,Fproducts such as gardening and DIY,
OL,10,Fall of which will help shoppers as
OL,11,Fthey manage their household budgets.
OL,13,F"With the potential for increased
OL,14,Fdemand during the summer of sport,
OL,15,Fretailers will be looking to keep
OL,16,Fprices as low as possible for as long
OL,17,Fas possible."
