PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782776882
OL,3,CShop price inflation remains unchanged
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of Middle East knock-
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FThe figures follow oil prices dropping
OL,8,Fto levels last seen before the war in
OL,9,Fthe Middle East as the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz reopens gradually following the
OL,11,FUS-Iran peace deal.
OL,13,FIt sparks hope of easing cost-of-
OL,14,Fliving pressures as prices begin
OL,15,Fretreating at the petrol pumps thanks
OL,16,Fto the drops in wholesale cost of
OL,17,Fcrude.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
