FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782776882
OL,3,CShop price inflation remains unchanged
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of Middle East knock-
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FThe declines follow last week's
OL,8,Finterim agreement to end the war and
OL,9,Fthe reopening of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,10,Fthrough which a fifth of the world's
OL,11,Foil and gas is normally shipped.
OL,13,FThe US and Iran signed a memorandum of
OL,14,Funderstanding on Friday lasting 60
OL,15,Fdays, which has seen the US partially
OL,16,Flift sanctions on Iranian oil exports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
